{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.1","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:1","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.007.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">R\u00e9ponse aux questions des Corinthiens sur les viandes sacrifi\u00e9es aux idoles<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-13: cf. 1 Co 10:19-33. Ro 14:13-23.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Pour ce qui concerne les viandes sacrifi\u00e9es aux idoles, nous savons que nous avons tous la connaissance. La connaissance enfle, mais la charit\u00e9 \u00e9difie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.2","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.7.40","name":"1 Corinthiens 7:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.7.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.2","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:2","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.008.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Si quelqu\u2019un croit savoir quelque chose, il n\u2019a pas encore connu comme il faut conna\u00eetre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.3","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.1","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.3","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:3","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.008.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Mais si quelqu\u2019un aime Dieu, celui-l\u00e0 est connu de lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.4","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.2","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.4","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:4","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.008.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Pour ce qui est donc de manger des viandes sacrifi\u00e9es aux idoles, nous savons qu\u2019il n\u2019y a point d\u2019idole dans le monde, et qu\u2019il n\u2019y a qu\u2019un seul Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.5","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.3","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.5","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:5","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.008.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Car, s\u2019il est des \u00eatres qui sont appel\u00e9s dieux, soit dans le ciel, soit sur la terre, comme il existe r\u00e9ellement plusieurs dieux et plusieurs seigneurs,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.6","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.4","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.6","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:6","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.008.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>n\u00e9anmoins pour nous il n\u2019y a qu\u2019un seul Dieu, le P\u00e8re, de qui viennent toutes choses et pour qui nous sommes, et un seul Seigneur, J\u00e9sus-Christ, par qui sont toutes choses et par qui nous sommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.5","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.7","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:7","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.008.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Mais cette connaissance n\u2019est pas chez tous. Quelques-uns, d\u2019apr\u00e8s la mani\u00e8re dont ils envisagent encore l\u2019idole, mangent de ces viandes comme \u00e9tant sacrifi\u00e9es aux idoles, et leur conscience, qui est faible, en est souill\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.6","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.8","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:8","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.008.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Ce n\u2019est pas un aliment qui nous rapproche de Dieu: si nous en mangeons, nous n\u2019avons rien de plus; si nous n\u2019en mangeons pas, nous n\u2019avons rien de moins.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.9","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.9","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:9","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.008.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Prenez garde, toutefois, que votre libert\u00e9 ne devienne une pierre d\u2019achoppement pour les faibles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.10","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.10","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:10","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.008.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Car, si quelqu\u2019un te voit, toi qui as de la connaissance, assis \u00e0 table dans un temple d\u2019idoles, sa conscience, \u00e0 lui qui est faible, ne le portera-t-elle pas \u00e0 manger des viandes sacrifi\u00e9es aux idoles?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.11","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.9","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.11","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:11","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.008.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et ainsi le faible p\u00e9rira par ta connaissance, le fr\u00e8re pour lequel Christ est mort!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.12","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.10","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.12","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:12","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.008.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.008.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>En p\u00e9chant de la sorte contre les fr\u00e8res, et en blessant leur conscience faible, vous p\u00e9chez contre Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.13","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.11","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.13","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 8:13","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.008.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.009.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.8.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi, si un aliment scandalise mon fr\u00e8re, je ne mangerai jamais de viande, afin de ne pas scandaliser mon fr\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.9.1","name":"1 Corinthiens 9:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.9.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.8.12","name":"1 Corinthiens 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.8.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb8d31081.24589358');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb8d31081.24589358\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb8d31081.24589358","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb8d31081.24589358'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb8d31081.24589358\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}